RCP 8.5 Relative Change

RCP 8.5 is a scenario that assumes very little reduction in greenhouse gas emissions, resulting in a high level of warming and significant sea level rise.

Below you can view the absolute and relative change maps. Check the Map Description for information about the creation of the map, especially the creation of the bins. Note that Change relates to differences between the time period 2070-2100 to today. We express calories in People Fed Yearly (PFY)
